**** THE COLOR PICKING GAME ****

**Description:
    In this game the user will see an RGB code displayed in the top part of the page. He/she must click the color that matches that
    code in order to win. After selecting the correct color a message will be displayed.
    
**Usage:
    
    RESET: Resets the game to its original state;
    EASY: Displays only 3 colors from which the user will have to choose;
    HARD: Displays 6 colors from which the user will have to choose;
